publisher			REL Games							
publish_time	 2005年3月28日		
desc_long								关于这款游戏							Deadhunt is a first-person arcade shooter (FPS) game that merges the best features of arcade and FPS action games with fresh ideas and new twists.An addictive 3D-shooter game where you consistently develop your character by killing endless monsters and getting bonuses. Stay as long as possible on fighting pits against hordes of zombies and skeletons.Features:- Non-stop adrenaline-pumping gameplay- 4 episodes with total of 40 missions- Two additional modes: Survival and Greed- Armed combat against multiple enemies- Three classes of monsters with 50 kinds of weapons- Unique system of monster destruction- Seven varieties of weapons plus grenades- 10 runes and 37 bonuses, including Slowdown, Double Damage, Nuke- Remote picking of bonuses, runes and weapons- 10 varieties of monsters' armor- 15 original soundtracks- Four difficulty levels***The game was released in 2005.						
title	 Deadhunt			
